high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of you.
Retrieve a plate from the cabiniet under the sink and close it afterwards.
Move to the middle of the sink in front of you.
Place and clean the plate in the sink with water, turn the water off and pick up the plate.
Move to the counter on the left side of the stove.
Place the plate on the wooden shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned plate from under the sink on the wooden self.

high_descs: Move forward then turn right to face the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink, pick up the dirty plate in there.
Bring the dirty plate to the sink.
Wash the dirty plate in the sink with water.
Pick up the cleaned plate from the sink, turn around, and move to the wooded rack past the counter on the right.
Put the cleaned plate on the middle wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned plate on the middle wooden rack.

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink and take out a plate.
Move slightly to the right.
Wash the plate in the sink.
Turn around and go to the shelf.
Put the plate on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed plate on the shelf.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the right
Get dirty plate from the cabinet
Move to the front of the sink
Clean plate in the sink
Move to the wooden self to the left of the stove
Put plate on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned plate on the wooden shelf.

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink and take out the plate.
Back up from the cupboard and focus on the sink.
Put the plate in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the plate up again.
Turn around and cross the room to face the brown shelves to the right of the counter.
Put the plate on the middle shelf on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on a shelf.

high_descs: Head to the sink that is ahead of you on your right.
Open the cabinet that is under the sink and pick up the dirty plate that is inside, then close the cabinet
Step left and continue to face the sink
Place the plate into the sink and turn on the faucet, then turn off the faucet and pick up the clean plate
Turn around and cross the room, then hang right and walk to the brown shelf
Place the clean plate on the middle shelf to the right of the clear vase.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean plate on a shelf
